What you need to know:  The late Mr Too’s family suffered a blow and lost control of the land in dispute following a landmark ruling on November 2022, by the Court of AppealAccording to the squatters, already 300 acres of the land has been hived off and is being cultivated, despite a court orderOut of the 25,000 acres that the family has claimed, the court only granted it 67.5 acresAppellate court described the acquisition of the land as a “misrepresentation and fraudulent”